Features: Operative L-shaped desk with an 18mm thick wooden top in laminate finish with PVC lipping.
Based on metal structure and one rectangular metal legs formed from 1.Smm metal sheets in electrostatic powder coated paint.
Attached side includes 3 lockable drawers & cabinet with lockable leaf open storage spaces.
Available with front modesty panel in laminate finish (Optional).
Including concealed cable management system with aluminum flap.
Excluding electric source and grommet power outlet.
Can be matched with corresponding pedestal; credenza and coffee table.

Dimensions: STANDARD DIMENSIONS: LXWXH 150x70x75 CM Right Or Left side
